网上的案例，担心往后发展就会一地鸡毛<br />2 、她胆子太小了，比如不敢去见我的家人甚至朋友，下班之后没人和她一起她就不敢出门等，我担心以后遇到事情的时候她没办法和我共度难关<br />3 、她和我年龄的差距<br />4 、她比较挑食，非常瘦，很多人看见她都会让她多吃点，我担心她的身体状况<br />5 、刚还完房贷，手里没存款，还有 7W 左右的负债，每月到手 8K ，没钱办婚礼这些<br /><br /><br />他闺蜜今天陪她去医院去了，我现在还不知道她的想法，请教各位 Ver 的意见，是保持现状还是往前迈一步把孩子留下来", "last_modified": 1778404716, "replies": 70, "id": 1211648}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 23258, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3664, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 381018, "username": "Moonkin", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Moonkin", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/53e2/015e/381018_mini.png?m=1768737929", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/53e2/015e/381018_normal.png?m=1768737929", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/53e2/015e/381018_large.png?m=1768737929", "created": 1548827950, "last_modified": 1768737929, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "zerovoid", "last_touched": 1778444043, "title": "我有一招可以在裁员潮的当下反击你的老板，并提高自身竞争力。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1211625", "created": 1778392985, "deleted": 0, "content": "那就是用 AI 把前公司的产品搓出来，可以是个 lite 版，挑高品质功能/内容。然后开源。\r\n\r\n你的前司再想搞一些奇怪的收费方式的时候，可能就会有人选择你这个开源竞品了。\r\n\r\n你还可以麒麟 OS+国密，更有竞争力，而且也不难，golang 写的，别用 cgo ，都可以在麒麟上面跑。目标系统也可以微信小程序。\r\n\r\n这样你至少积累了项目经验，其次出了口气。因为有 ai 在，这些也不难，你也可以多一些 AI 经验。\r\n\r\n这样你的前司就属于是 成也 AI ，败也 AI 。", "content_rendered": "<p>那就是用 AI 把前公司的产品搓出来，可以是个 lite 版，挑高品质功能/内容。然后开源。</p>\n<p>你的前司再想搞一些奇怪的收费方式的时候，可能就会有人选择你这个开源竞品了。</p>\n<p>你还可以麒麟 OS+国密，更有竞争力，而且也不难，golang 写的，别用 cgo ，都可以在麒麟上面跑。目标系统也可以微信小程序。</p>\n<p>这样你至少积累了项目经验，其次出了口气。因为有 ai 在，这些也不难，你也可以多一些 AI 经验。</p>\n<p>这样你的前司就属于是 成也 AI ，败也 AI 。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1778408089, "replies": 56, "id": 1211625}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 23258, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3664, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 587690, "username": "cwwx2022", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/cwwx2022", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0aab/72eb/587690_mini.png?m=1778069519", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0aab/72eb/587690_normal.png?m=1778069519", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0aab/72eb/587690_large.png?m=1778069519", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0aab/72eb/587690_xlarge.png?m=1778069519", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0aab/72eb/587690_xxlarge.png?m=1778069519", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0aab/72eb/587690_xxxlarge.png?m=1778069519", "created": 1657605292, "last_modified": 1778069519, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "clearlove13", "last_touched": 1778428832, "title": "我就想知道 2026 年失业的都是哪些人？我 1 月 8 日失业的", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1211582", "created": 1778376159, "deleted": 0, "content": "降薪调岗或者自己离职让我选", "content_rendered": "降薪调岗或者自己离职让我选", "last_modified": 1778377956, "replies": 45, "id": 1211582}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal